OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1776971469
OL,3,CCamera traps used in search for
OL,4,Cmissing capybara 'stolen'
OL,6,FCamera traps being used in the search
OL,7,Ffor a capybara missing from Marwell
OL,8,FZoo have been stolen, according to
OL,9,Fstaff.
OL,11,FSamba, a nine-month-old capybara,
OL,12,Fescaped from her enclosure after she
OL,13,Farrived from Jimmy's Farm and Wildlife
OL,14,FPark in Suffolk with fellow capybara
OL,15,FTango in March.
OL,17,FBoth capybaras - which are the world's
OL,18,Flargest rodents - managed to escape
OL,19,Falthough Tango was quickly recaptured.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
