FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1776971469
OL,3,CCamera traps used in search for
OL,4,Cmissing capybara 'stolen'
OL,6,FSamba remains at large despite the use
OL,7,Fof thermal drones, camera traps and
OL,8,Fappeals to the public for help.
OL,10,FNow Marwell Zoo chief executive Laura
OL,11,FReed has said that two camera traps
OL,12,Fhad been stolen as she appealed for
OL,13,Fpeople to continue to keep an eye out
OL,14,Ffor Samba.
OL,16,FShe said: "Over the last weeks since
OL,17,FSamba disappeared, we have received a
OL,18,Fnumber of reported sightings of her
OL,19,Ffrom members of the public.
OL,26,@xD@KOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1776971469
OL,3,CCamera traps used in search for
OL,4,Cmissing capybara 'stolen'
OL,6,F"We are extremely grateful to everyone
OL,7,Fwho is supporting us and has taken the
OL,8,Ftime to get in touch with their
OL,9,Finformation.
OL,11,F"Sadly, despite thorough follow-ups on
OL,12,Fthese reports, none has yet resulted
OL,13,Fin a confirmed sighting of Samba.
OL,15,F"Our teams remain fully committed and
OL,16,Fcontinue to carry out searches of the
OL,17,Farea.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1776971469
OL,3,CCamera traps used in search for
OL,4,Cmissing capybara 'stolen'
OL,6,F"We are still using thermal drone
OL,7,Ftechnology and camera traps in key
OL,8,Fareas where Samba is most likely to
OL,9,Ftravel, particularly along waterways
OL,10,Fand dense vegetation.
OL,12,F"We are however facing a number of
OL,13,Fchallenges.
OL,15,F"Unfortunately, two of our camera
OL,16,Ftraps have been stolen which is
OL,17,Fhampering our search.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1776971469
OL,3,CCamera traps used in search for
OL,4,Cmissing capybara 'stolen'
OL,6,F"We're also aware that some of the
OL,7,Freported sightings of Samba may
OL,8,Factually be Muntjac deer as they are
OL,9,Ffound in the area and are of a similar
OL,10,Fsize and colouring.
OL,12,F"Despite these difficulties and
OL,13,FSamba's natural capybara instinct to
OL,14,Fstay hidden, we are not giving up our
OL,15,Fsearch and remain focused on bringing
OL,16,Fher home safely."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@QO]
